\c 27
\s UPawuli uya eRoma eyisibotshwa
\p
\v 1 Kwathi sekuqunyiwe ukuthi siye eIthaliya ngomkhumbi\x + 25.12,25.\x*, banikela uPawuli lezinye izibotshwa ezithile enduneni yekhulu, nguJuliyu ngebizo, eyesigaba senkosi enkulu\x + Joha. 18.3.\x*.
\v 2 Sasesingena emkhunjini weAdramithiyu, obusuzakuya endaweni zangaseAsiya\x + 2.9.\x*, saqala ukuhamba, uAristako umMakedoniya\x + 19.29.\x* weThesalonika wayelathi\x + 20.4. 17.1.\x*.
\v 3 Lakusisa safika eSidoni\x + Luka 4.26.\x*; uJuliyu wasemphatha kuhle uPawuli\x + 28.2.\x*, wa\add m\add*vumela ukuthi aye kubangane ukuze asizwe\x + 24.23. 28.16.\x*.
\v 4 Sasesisuka lapho ngomkhumbi\x + 27.7. 21.3. 27.5.\x* sehla sagudla iKuprosi\x + 4.36.\x*, ngoba imimoya yayiphambene \add lathi\add*,
\v 5 kwathi sesidabule ulwandle olungaseKilikhiya lePamfiliya, safika eMira yeLikhiya.
\v 6 Lapho-ke induna yekhulu yathola umkhumbi weAleksandriya oya eIthaliya, yasikhweza kuwo\x + 28.11. 6.9.\x*.
\v 7 Sasesihamba kancinyane okwensuku ezinengi, safika nzima maqondana leKinidu, umoya ungasivumeli\x + 27.4.\x*, sehla sagudla\x + 27.7. 21.3. 27.5.\x* iKrete\x + 27.12,13,21. 2.10.\x* maqondana leSalamone;
\v 8 sasesiyigudla\x + 27.13.\x* kanzima safika endaweni ethile ethiwa yiMathekwamahle; okwakuseduze layo umuzi iLaseya.
\p
\v 9 Kwathi sekudlule isikhathi esikhulu, njalo sekuyingozi ukuhamba ngomkhumbi, ngoba lezilo lokudla laseledlule, uPawuli wa\add be\add*luleka
\v 10 esithi kubo: Madoda, ngiyabona ukuthi uhambo luzakuba lengozi\x + 27.21.\x* lomonakalo omkhulu\x + 27.21.\x*, kungeyisiwo owempahla lomkhumbi kuphela kodwa lowempilo zethu.
\v 11 Kodwa induna yekhulu yakholwa induna yomkhumbi lomnikazi wawo kulezinto ezazitshiwo nguPawuli\x + Isam. 18.17.\x*.
\v 12 Kwathi njengoba itheku lalingalungelanga ukuhlalwa ebusika, inengi labo lacebisa ukuthi kusukwe lalapho, mhlawumbe kwenzeke ukuthi bafike eFenikisi bahlale \add khona\add* ebusika, itheku leKrete\x + 27.12,13,21. 2.10.\x* elikhangele eningizimuntshonalanga lenyakathontshonalanga.
\p
\v 13 Njalo kuthe umoya weningizimu usuphephetha buthakathaka, banakana ukuthi sebekuzuzile lokho ababekuqondile, sebephakamise \add ingwegwe\add* sagudla eKrete.
\v 14 Kodwa kungabanga \add yisikhathi\add* eside umoya oyisivunguzane, othiwa iYurakilidoni, wawutshaya;
\v 15 umkhumbi wasubanjwa, wehluleka ukukhangelana lomoya, sasesiwuyekela undenda.
\v 16 Sathi sesigudla phansi kwesihlengana esithile esithiwa yiKlawuda, senelisa kalukhuni ukuwubamba umkolo;
\v 17 abathi sebewuphanyekile, basebenzisa izincediso, babopha ngamagoda azingelezela umkhumbi; basebesesaba ukuthi bazaphoseka eSirtisi, behlisa iseyili, ngokunjalo basebendenda\x + 27.26,29.\x*.
\v 18 Kuthe ukuthi siphoswe kakhulu yisiphepho, ngo\add lu\add*landelayo baphosa impahla\x + Jona 1.5.\x*;
\v 19 kwathi ngolwesithathu salahla izikhali zomkhumbi ngezandla zethu uqobo\x + Jona 1.5.\x*.
\v 20 Kwathi kungelalanga njalo kungelankanyezi ezibonakalayo insuku ezinengi, lesiphepho esingesincinyane \add si\add*qinisa, kusukela lapho laseliphela ithemba lonke lokuthi sizasinda.
\p
\v 21 Kwathi sekuyisikhathi eside bengasadli, uPawuli wasesukuma phakathi kwabo, wathi: Madoda, ngabe lalalela mina\x + 27.10.\x* kalaze lasuka eKrete\x + 27.12,13,21. 2.10.\x*, njalo laphepha kulobubunzima\x + 27.21.\x* lakulumonakalo\x + 27.21.\x*.
\v 22 Khathesi-ke sengileluleka ukuthi lime isibindi; ngoba kakusoze kulahleke impilo leyodwa kini, ngaphandle komkhumbi.
\v 23 Ngoba\x + 18.9. 23.11. 12.7.\x* ngalobubusuku bekumi kimi ingilosi kaNkulunkulu, engingowakhe\x + 2 Tim. 4.17.\x*, lengimkhonzayo\x + 24.14. Roma 1.9. 2 Tim. 1.3. Dan. 6.16. Luka 1.74. Fil. 3.3. Heb. 9.14. 12.28.\x*,
\v 24 yathi: Ungesabi Pawuli; ngoba umele ukuma phambi kukaKesari; njalo khangela, uNkulunkulu ukuphile bonke labo abahamba ngomkhumbi lawe\x + 25.11,16. Luka 7.42.\x*.
\v 25 Ngakho manini isibindi madoda\x + 27.22,36.\x*; ngoba ngiyakholwa kuNkulunkulu ukuthi kuzakuba njengalokho engikutsheliweyo\x + Luka 1.45.\x*.
\v 26 Kodwa kumele\x + 28.1.\x* sitshayeke esihlengeni esithile\x + 27.17,29,32.\x*.
\p
\v 27 Kwathi sekufike ubusuku betshumi lane, sasindenda sizula olwandle lweAdriya, phakathi kobusuku, abomkhumbi bakhumbula ukuthi umhlabathi othile ususondela kubo;
\v 28 basebephosa intambo yokulinganisa bathola \w amafathome\w** angamatshumi amabili; sebeqhubekile kancinyane baphosa intambo yokulinganisa futhi, bathola amafathome alitshumi lanhlanu;
\v 29 njalo sesaba ukuthi mhlawumbe singatshayeka emadwaleni, basebephosela ingwegwe ezine ngemva komkhumbi, bafisa ukuthi kuse\x + 27.17,29,32.\x*.
\v 30 Abomkhumbi sebezama ukubaleka emkhunjini, basebesehlisela olwandle umkolo\x + 27.16.\x* ngokungathi basebezakwehlisela ingwegwe ngaphambi komkhumbi\x + Joha. 15.22.\x*,
\v 31 uPawuli wathi enduneni yekhulu lakwabebutho: Uba laba bengahlali emkhunjini, lingesindiswe lina.
\v 32 Abebutho basebequma amagoda omkolo\x + Joha. 2.15.\x*, bawuyekela\x + 27.40. 5.38.\x* wawa\x + 27.17,29,32.\x*.
\p
\v 33 Kwasekusithi sekuzakusa, uPawuli wa\add ba\add*ncenga bonke ukuthi bathathe ukudla, esithi: Lamuhla kulusuku lwetshumi lane lilindile lihlezi lingadli, lingathathi lutho.
\v 34 Ngakho ngiyalincenga ukuthi lithathe ukudla; ngoba lokhu ngokosindiso lwenu; ngoba kakuyikuwa komunye unwele lwekhanda lenu\x + 1 Sam. 14.45.\x*.
\v 35 Kwathi esetshilo lezizinto, esethethe isinkwa, wabonga uNkulunkulu phambi kwabo bonke; wa\add si\add*hlephula waqala ukudla\x + Mat. 15.36.\x*.
\v 36 Basebesima isibindi bonke njalo bona bathatha ukudla\x + 27.22,36.\x*.
\v 37 Njalo thina sonke esasisemkhunjini sasiyimiphefumulo engamakhulu amabili lamatshumi ayisikhombisa lesithupha\x + 2.41. 7.14. 1 Pet. 3.20. Roma 13.1. Jak. 5.20.\x*.
\v 38 Njalo sebesuthi ukudla baphungula umkhumbi, baphosela amabele olwandle.
\p
\v 39 Kwathi sekusile, kabalazanga ilizwe; kodwa babona itheku elithile lilokhumbi, abamisa ukuthi baqhubele umkhumbi kulo, uba kungenzeka.
\v 40 Basebequma ingwegwe ba\add zi\add*yekela olwandle\x + 27.29.\x*, ngesikhathi esifananayo bathukulula amagoda abophe amaphini okuqondisa, baphakamisela emoyeni iseyili yaphambili baqonda ekhunjini\x + 27.17.\x*.
\v 41 Basebefika bengananzelele endaweni lapho ulwandle olwaluhlangana khona bawuqhubela umkhumbi esihlabathini; njalo isihloko somkhumbi sagxumekeka sahlala singanyikinyeki, kodwa ingemuva yomkhumbi yephulwa ngamandla amagagasi\x + 2 Kor. 11.25.\x*.
\v 42 Labebutho babeqonde ukubulala izibotshwa, hlezi ezinye zibaleke ngokuntshezela khatshana.
\v 43 Kodwa induna yekhulu, ifisa ukusindisa uPawuli, yabavimbela kunjongo \add yabo\add*, yasilaya ukuthi labo abakwaziyo ukuntsheza baziphosele olwandle kuqala, baye emhlabathini;
\v 44 labaseleyo, abanye ngamapulanka, labanye ngezinye zezinto zomkhumbi. Ngokunjalo-ke kwenzeka ukuthi bonke bafike emhlabathini besindile\x + 27.22.\x*.